{"text_id":34201,"tokens":["We"," present"," a"," novel"," approach"," to"," the"," synthesis"," of"," Taylor"," phase"," screens",","," which"," uses"," Kar","h","unen","-","Lo","\u00e8ve"," (","KL",")"," basis"," functions"," to"," approximate"," the"," covariance"," function"," of"," the"," desired"," screen","."," Our"," motivation"," stems"," from"," the"," need"," to"," generate"," accurate"," and"," efficient"," phase"," screens"," for"," simulating"," atmospheric"," turbulence"," and"," optical"," wave"," propagation","."," The"," Taylor"," phase"," screen"," is"," a"," widely"," used"," model",","," but"," its"," traditional"," implementation"," using"," Zer","nike"," polynomials"," can"," be"," computationally"," intensive","."," By"," employing"," KL"," basis"," functions",","," we"," exploit"," the"," statistical"," properties"," of"," the"," desired"," screen"," to"," create"," a"," more"," efficient"," and"," flexible"," representation","."," Our"," methodology"," involves"," computing"," the"," KL"," basis"," functions"," from"," a"," target"," covariance"," function",","," then"," using"," them"," to"," synthesize"," the"," Taylor"," phase"," screen","."," We"," demonstrate"," the"," effectiveness"," of"," our"," approach"," through"," numerical"," simulations",","," which"," show"," that"," our"," KL","-","based"," phase"," screens"," accurately"," reproduce"," the"," statistics"," of"," the"," desired"," screen"," while"," requiring"," significantly"," less"," computational"," resources"," than"," traditional"," methods","."," The"," results"," have"," important"," implications"," for"," a"," range"," of"," applications",","," including"," optics",","," astronomy",","," and"," remote"," sensing","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-70b","label":1}